## 1) Goals

### 1.1 Customer goals
- Recommendations feel **accurate and respectful** (no pool offers for no pool).
- Adding services feels **easy and in-control** (one click, minimal friction).
- The app feels **personalized to my home**, not generic.
- Switching from existing vendors feels **safe and non-confrontational**.

### 1.2 Business goals
- Increase **attach rate** and **ARR per household** via relevant, context-aware add-ons.
- Improve conversion of “curious browsers” into “committed members” by showing tailored value.
- Reduce CAC amortized cost by expanding within the same household relationship.

### 1.3 Operational goals
- Improve Level default accuracy → fewer mismatches, fewer courtesy upgrades, fewer disputes.
- Reduce support load by preventing scope surprises through better sizing.
- Keep ops scalable: rules-driven, minimal manual intervention.

