## 2) Non-goals (v1 of 3B)
- Exact sqft pulls from third-party data providers (may come later)
- Counting windows via AI/vision
- Hard enforcement of “minimum level” (we’ll collect signals first; enforce later if needed)
- Any major Home tab or Add Service Drawer redesign (that’s 3C)

