## 8) Personalization API Contract (important for later sprints)
Define a single function (or service) that returns the normalized signals used by UI and engines:

### 8.1 `get_property_profile_context(property_id)`
Returns:
```json
{
  "property_id": "uuid",
  "coverage": {
    "pool": { "status": "NA", "switch_intent": null },
    "windows": { "status": "NONE", "switch_intent": null },
    "lawn": { "status": "PROVIDER", "switch_intent": "OPEN_LATER" }
  },
  "sizing": {
    "home_sqft_tier": "2500_3500",
    "yard_tier": "MED",
    "windows_tier": "15_30",
    "stories_tier": "2"
  },
  "computed": {
    "eligible_categories": ["windows","gutters","trash_bins", "..."],
    "suppressed_categories": ["pool"],
    "high_confidence_upsells": ["trash_bins","gutters"],
    "switch_candidates": ["lawn"]
  }
}
````

This becomes the backbone for 3C (Add Service Drawer + Home restructure) without context explosion.

