## 13) Opinionated UX Notes (to maximize the “one-tap OS” feel)

* Use language that reinforces your brand promise:

  * “Help us tailor your home.”
  * “This prevents irrelevant suggestions.”
* Avoid asking for exact counts (windows, sqft). Use tiers.
* Don’t ask for vendor names. That feels invasive and slows completion.
* Make “Not applicable” highly visible (especially pool, yard) to prevent dumb suggestions forever.

